### 3. 🔴 No Global Error Handler
Unhandled errors will expose stack traces to clients, leaking internal implementation details.

**Fix:** Add a centralized error-handling middleware at the end of all routes:
```js
// eslint-disable-next-line no-unused-vars
app.use((err, req, res, next) => {
